verbose_text: Results showed that one shot of PLG-rSAG1/2 MPs or oil formulation rSAG1/2 (Vet L-10) could elicit IgG antibodies to react to the native SAG1 (30 kDa) and SAG2 (22 kDa) in TsoAg (XREF_FIG, lanes 1 and 2), which were also, respectively, recognized by the TG-1 and TG-2 mAbs (XREF_FIG, lanes 7 and 8).
evidence: Vet L-10) could elicit IgG antibodies
